headline: Q4 Earnings Highlights: Greenbrier (NYSE:GBX) Vs The Rest Of The Heavy Transportation Equipment Stocks
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Greenbrier (NYSE:GBX) and the rest of the heavy transportation equipment stocks fared in Q4.
